definition: he or him/(used for either sex when the sex is unknown or unimportant)/(used before sb's name for emphasis)/(used as a meaningless mock object)/other/another
prefecture/(old) province/(old) administrative division/state (e.g. of US)/oblast (Russia)/canton (Switzerland)

sentences.english: Former governor of Utah, Jon Huntsman, is running for president.
sentences.chinese: 前犹他州长洪博培宣布竞选总统。

sentences.english: One is called the City Center Lofts in Salt Lake City, Utah.
sentences.chinese: 一个称为城市阁楼，坐落在犹他州盐湖城。

sentences.english: Park City and Snowbird in Utah let some children ski free.
sentences.chinese: 犹他州的公园城市和雪鸟让一些儿童免费滑雪。

sentences.english: Dark clouds roll over Paria Canyon- Vermillion Cliffs Wilderness in Utah.
sentences.chinese: 乌云向犹他州帕里亚峡谷的黄石公园席卷而来。

sentences.english: for photo of Northern Harriers, Bear River Migratory Bird Refuge, UT
sentences.chinese: 这张白尾鹞照片摄于犹他州贝尔河候鸟保护地。

sentences.english: Don’t do it in Utah, where it’s supposedly illegal.
sentences.chinese: 在犹他州不要这样做，这种行为在那里是非法的。

sentences.english: Two hikers in the Narrows, Zion National Park, Utah.
sentences.chinese: 在犹他州峡口的宰恩国家公园里的两个徒步旅行者。

sentences.english: Ron Artest converted every person from Utah into Rockets fans.
sentences.chinese: 阿泰把所有犹他州的人变成火箭迷。

sentences.english: In Utah, discovering a band of polygamists hardly raises an eyebrow.
sentences.chinese: 在犹他州发现一伙重婚者不足为奇。

sentences.english: He has got the bachelor of medicament and doctor of medicine from salt lake city university, utah.
sentences.chinese: 获犹他州盐湖城大学的药剂学士和医学博士学位。

sentences.english: This area has been designed as Non-Smoking Per the Utah Clean Air Act.
sentences.chinese: 根据犹他州空气清洁法令，此区设为无烟区。

sentences.english: The lake, near the city of Provo, is the largest natural body of freshwater in the state.
sentences.chinese: 该湖位于普罗沃附近，是犹他州最大的天然淡水湖。

sentences.english: This area has been designated as Non-Smoking Per the Utah Clean Air Act.
sentences.chinese: 根据犹他州空气洁净法令，此区设为无烟区。

sentences.english: Here is a photo from Dead Horse Point State Park in Utah.
sentences.chinese: 照片是从犹他州的死马角州立公园这个方位拍摄的。

sentences.english: I even moved to Utah to be with him.
sentences.chinese: 我甚至搬到了犹他州，为了和他在一起。
